  32:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   (+) Interrupt generation at the end of regular conversion, end of injected
  33:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****       conversion, and in case of analog watchdog or overrun events.
  34:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   
  35:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   (+) Single and continuous conversion modes.
  36:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   
  37:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   (+) Scan mode for conversion of several channels sequentially.
  38:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   
  39:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   (+) Data alignment with in-built data coherency.
  40:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   
  41:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   (+) Programmable sampling time (channel wise)
  42:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   
  43:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   (+) ADC conversion of regular group and injected group.
  44:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c **** 
