  49:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c **** 
  50:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   (+) Multimode Dual mode (available on devices with 2 ADCs or more).
  51:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   
