  53:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****       with 2 DCs or more).
  54:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   
  55:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   (+) Configurable delay between conversions in Dual interleaved mode (available 
  56:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****       on devices with 2 DCs or more).
  57:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   
