 559:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****     /*   0x00: 1 channel converted (channel on regular rank 1)                */
 560:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****     /*   Parameter "NbrOfConversion" is discarded.                            */
