1529:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c **** /**
1530:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @brief  Enables ADC, starts conversion of regular group and transfers result
1531:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         through DMA.
1532:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         Interruptions enabled in this function:
1533:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *          - DMA transfer complete
1534:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *          - DMA half transfer
1535:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         Each of these interruptions has its dedicated callback function.
1536:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @note   For devices with several ADCs: This function is for single-ADC mode 
1537:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         only. For multimode, use the dedicated MultimodeStart function.
1538:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @note   On STM32F1 devices, only ADC1 and ADC3 (ADC availability depending
1539:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         on devices) have DMA capability.
1540:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         ADC2 converted data can be transferred in dual ADC mode using DMA
1541:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         of ADC1 (ADC master in multimode).
1542:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         In case of using ADC1 with DMA on a device featuring 2 ADC
1543:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         instances: ADC1 conversion register DR contains ADC1 conversion 
1544:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         result (ADC1 register DR bits 0 to 11) and, additionally, ADC2 last
1545:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         conversion result (ADC1 register DR bits 16 to 27). Therefore, to
1546:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         have DMA transferring the conversion results of ADC1 only, DMA must
1547:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   *         be configured to transfer size: half word.
ARM GAS  C:\WINDOWS\ccjOB5ii.s 			page 38


1548:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @param  hadc: ADC handle
1549:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @param  pData: The destination Buffer address.
