2284:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c **** /**
2285:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @brief  Stop ADC conversion and disable the selected ADC
2286:./f103/HAL/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_adc.c ****   * @note   Prerequisite condition to use this function: ADC conversions must be
